VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)\b(urllib2|commands)\b
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:urllib2|commands\.getoutput|commands\.getstatusoutput|urllib\.urlopen && MISSING:test|example|migration|legacy
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the use of deprecated Python functions and modules.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Deprecated Python Functions.
